                Mana mana)
        The constructor of Monster class
        参数:
        type - The type of the monster.
        hp - The health of the monster.
        speed - The speed at which the monster moves.
        armour - The armor rating of the monster.
        mana_gained_on_kill - The amount of mana gained when the monster is killed.
        mana - The Mana object associated with the monster for mana management.
